{"tid":1955083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【日落帝國】英國近95萬人過去兩周武漢肺炎疫情下申領福利救濟金","createTime":"2020-04-02T09:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T15:50:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c822bed4ab833002e6bff32e0c0f0ba29dc09e2","tid":1955083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"英國政府因為武漢肺炎檢測安排，在國內繼續受到廣泛批評。報道說在英格蘭地區，約50萬名前線醫護人員中，只有約2000人接受過病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜早前承諾，英國需要大規模增加檢測次數。工黨要求政府在病毒檢測政策上，增加透明度，釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去兩星期英國近95萬人，在武漢肺炎疫情下申領福利救濟金。英國航空據報與工會達成協議，安排約36000名僱員暫時停工，涉及近八成機艙服務員、地勤人員、工程師及總部工作人員。根據協議，公司不會裁員。"},{"pid":"e8cd8aa6352b5f1f40f502912f932ccabcb306a7","tid":1955083,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"關日落咩事<br />\n香港人一個仙都冇，英國咁快有錢"},{"pid":"8ee178652f79c7a474e875e2da1b2add8d7f0954","tid":1955083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8cd8aa6352b5f1f40f502912f932ccabcb306a7","tid":1955083,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"關日落咩事<br />\n香港人一個仙都冇，英國咁快有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"相等於香港失業綜援"},{"pid":"7ac209357599bb6cbe70d8fd09fc4efcc3ed70fe","tid":1955083,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"525c1f4b420e16bac911385329cabe47da38d765","tid":1955083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ac209357599bb6cbe70d8fd09fc4efcc3ed70fe","tid":1955083,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"失業綜援"},{"pid":"baf73699f66fb4a60242a78cee6c81282654d137","tid":1955083,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8cd8aa6352b5f1f40f502912f932ccabcb306a7","tid":1955083,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"關日落咩事<br />\n香港人一個仙都冇，英國咁快有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"申領, 唔係即時到手架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4113dc82c20892ec12eef25ee9e8c6d51455f08","tid":1955083,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"借個位一推<br />\n<br />\n(英國戰線)鄭文傑Simon Cheng呼籲大家捐錢支持英國對付疫情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1955676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1955676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}